import { Box, Grommet, Tab, Tabs, Form, FormField, Button, TextInput } from 'grommet';
import React from 'react';

export default function TabsForm (props) {

    return(
        <Box pad="small">
        <Tabs>
            <Tab title={props.title} tabIndex="1">
                <Box justify="center" pad="small">
                    <Box direction="column" alignSelf="center"  border={{ color: 'brand', size: 'small' }} pad="small"> 
                        <Form key={1}>
                            <FormField label="Requestor" >
                            <TextInput placeholder="Enter Requestor" name="Device1" />
                            </FormField>
                            <FormField label="PR Number">
                            <TextInput placeholder="Enter PR Number" name="Device2" />
                            </FormField>
                            <FormField label="PO Number" >
                            <TextInput placeholder="Enter PO Number" name="Device3" />
                            </FormField>
                            <Button key={1} type="submit" primary label="Submit" />
                        </Form>
                    </Box> 
                </Box> 
            </Tab>
        </Tabs>
        </Box>
    ); 
}
